{"tid":511242,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"[個鼻好痕]lala徐佳瑩集中討論post (2) 第5張 全新專輯 心理學 2017","createTime":"2017-12-27T09:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T09:45:58.000Z","uid":42332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"727fb6fe3a2fd5e60298757da1d41f1311c0cf61","tid":511242,"uid":42332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Lala is the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/161612_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F161612_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=461a659d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新碟 心理學</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/164046_2cd6b38f7d7353f40d7b2575822d7c8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F164046_2cd6b38f7d7353f40d7b2575822d7c8f.jpg&h=e26aeca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>主打歌 言不由衷</strong></span></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/233116_e561c481b44a53094318d1220e34f23b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F233116_e561c481b44a53094318d1220e34f23b.jpg&h=ef331974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k8jAqe9QZ7I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk8jAqe9QZ7I&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=3c585de3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k8jAqe9QZ7I</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>2.\t灰色</strong></div></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/121813_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F121813_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1b4aa4fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xtSdgGHqnls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxtSdgGHqnls&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=aace711e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xtSdgGHqnls</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3.\t到此為止<br />\n4.\t記得帶走<br />\n5.\t病人<br />\n6.\t現在不跳舞要幹嘛<br />\n7.\t大頭仔<br />\n8.\t兒歌<br />\n9.\t人啊<br />\n10.\t心裡學<br />\n11.\t是日救星 (特別收錄『是日救星』巡迴演唱會同名主題曲)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">徐佳瑩Lala 個人簡介</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n徐佳瑩（1984年12月20日－），生於臺灣臺中市，籍貫四川省簡陽縣，華語流行音樂創作女歌手、金曲獎得主。<br />\n<br />\n2008年，徐佳瑩參加中視第三屆《超級星光大道》歌唱選秀比賽，並於同年8月15日在總決賽中以自創詞曲作品奪得「總冠軍」而出道。2009年5月29日，徐佳瑩發行首張個人專輯《LaLa首張創作專輯》，迄今已正式發行5張個人專輯及2張演唱會專輯。<br />\n<br />\n2010年，徐佳瑩憑藉自己的首張個人專輯於第21屆金曲獎榮獲最佳新人獎，成為第一位從《超級星光大道》比賽畢業後獲得金曲獎的星光幫歌手。2015年，徐佳瑩以專輯《尋人啟事》入圍第26屆金曲獎六個獎項。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人專輯</strong><br />\n<br />\n1 ) 《LaLa首張創作專輯》2009年5月29日 <a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/wC31rDmmc1kGXdf0FVhU008l-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Falbum%2FwC31rDmmc1kGXdf0FVhU008l-index.html&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a124b68b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/wC31rDmmc1kGXdf0FVhU008l-index.html</a><br />\n2 ) 《極限》2010年9月3日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/f3G7viJnAVRmSTU0F.hm008l-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Falbum%2Ff3G7viJnAVRmSTU0F.hm008l-index.html&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9ee90c10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/f3G7viJnAVRmSTU0F.hm008l-index.html</a><br />\n3 ) 《理想人生》2012年6月6日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/0NtGh-oXVwgKG70F1H0m0091-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Falbum%2F0NtGh-oXVwgKG70F1H0m0091-index.html&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=65a8a814\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/0NtGh-oXVwgKG70F1H0m0091-index.html</a><br />\n4 ) 《尋人啟事》2014年6月13日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/6scbuNU.J19N4P0FF64q0091-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Falbum%2F6scbuNU.J19N4P0FF64q0091-index.html&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=21d843c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/6scbuNU.J19N4P0FF64q0091-index.html</a><br />\n5 ) 《心裡學》2017年12月27日 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/pNFsbrKpTgu3Q0F1qaKN009H-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Falbum%2FpNFsbrKpTgu3Q0F1qaKN009H-index.html&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=66e1b155\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/pNFsbrKpTgu3Q0F1qaKN009H-index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>演唱會</strong><br />\n1 ) 《繼續&middot;理想人生》2013年4月16日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/ZxuT72Nt1WHV2A0F38Cx0091-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Falbum%2FZxuT72Nt1WHV2A0F38Cx0091-index.html&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=40b8e042\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/ZxuT72Nt1WHV2A0F38Cx0091-index.html</a><br />\n2 ) 《日全蝕》2016年5月13日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/PBr7bh7mhLurB90FuSOo0091-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Falbum%2FPBr7bh7mhLurB90FuSOo0091-index.html&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7b6788b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/album/PBr7bh7mhLurB90FuSOo0091-index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>翻唱高手</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n我是歌手<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FuedTgMzSJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFuedTgMzSJQ&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1b917d1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FuedTgMzSJQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/a8JCtj1JBQs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fa8JCtj1JBQs&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=af8be554\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/a8JCtj1JBQs</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DZjkUlfnuM8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDZjkUlfnuM8&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=dd593c9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DZjkUlfnuM8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IBT0_3QUy98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIBT0_3QUy98&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=852f4d92\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IBT0_3QUy98</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成名歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />